{
  "chapter": 29,
  "chapter_summary": "无十三在泥泞空地上摆出只有一张胡床的盛宴，逼绝大师、铁震天等武林豪客坐在不存在的椅子上，吃不存在的佳肴。绝大师带头屈从，众人被荒诞恐惧压住，唯有铁震天不断以直言和机智相抗。无十三忽然栽赃冯超凡吃掉他的小狗，并以此设赌，实际命波斯奴出刀开膛剖腹。随后他弹黑石打穴，波斯奴弯刀连杀多人，场面惨烈。马如龙冲入刀光血光救人，拼死救回数人，回到杂货店后力竭倒下。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也想得要死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_bo_si_nu",
      "text": "你看还有没有别的客人会来？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bo_si_nu",
      "speaker_name": "波斯奴",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "我看没有了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请坐，请各位先入席坐下来再说话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "阁下为什么不坐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "我喜欢站着吃东西。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "站着吃才能吃得多些。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有理！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天各位一定要多吃些，今天我替各位准备了东海乌鱼，北海的鱼趣，南海的燕窝和龙虾，京城的羊羔和烤鸭，江南的醋鱼和蒸蟹，还有整只的牛羊，足够让各位开怀大嚼。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你为什么不吃一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "吃什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "羊羔和醋鱼的味道都很不错，",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "烤鸭也要趁热吃才好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "烤鸭在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "醋鱼在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你看不见？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "我看不见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "别人都看得见，你为什么看不见。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "因为我没有他们聪明，",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "你说的这些东西，一定只有聪明人才看得见。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "原来你是个呆子，这么多好吃的东西，只有呆子才看不见。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "你怎么能做这种事？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "我做了什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "有这么多好东西你不吃，为什么偏偏要吃我的小狗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "你的小狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "speaker_name": "冯超凡",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "你的小狗在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "刚才还在这里的，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "现在已经被你连皮带骨都吃了下去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "这条小狗我已经养了好几年，就像是我的儿子一样，你为什么要吃掉他？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_feng_chao_fan",
      "text": "为什么如此残忍？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "这里根本连一条狗都没有，",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "大狗小狗都没有。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你是呆子，你当然看不见。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我亲眼看见的，绝不会假的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "这次你恐怕看错了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你一定要说这里没有狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "绝对没有。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "可是我说有，而且已经被他吃进肚子！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你想不想跟我赌？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "text": "怎么赌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "赌那条小狗是不是在他肚子里，",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "无十三",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "用你的人头做赌注。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 29,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
